x4code.headerHelp: Digitizing error of outgoing particle energy

x4freetext: Digitizing error
Digitizing error
The accuracy of cross-section measurement was
determined by the errors of target thickness definition
(near 10%), integrator current calibration (near 3%),
solid angle of spectrometer (near 3%) and statistical
errors depending on the type and energy of particles
registered.
